"""
        Test that providing a custom list of cipher suites yields the right
        cipher string.
        """
suite = auth.TLS12AuthenticationSuite(['TLS_RSA_WITH_AES_256_CBC_SHA256',
    'TLS_RSA_WITH_AES_256_CBC_SHA', 'TLS_DHE_PSK_WITH_AES_128_CBC_SHA',
    'TLS_ECDHE_ECDSA_WITH_AES_128_CBC_SHA', 'DHE-DSS-AES256-SHA',
    'DHE-RSA-AES256-SHA'])
ciphers = suite.ciphers
self.assertIsInstance(ciphers, str)
suites = ciphers.split(':')
self.assertEqual(1, len(suites))
self.assertIn('AES256-SHA256', suites)
